[from fanqienovel.com and bkneng.com]

23
00:01:49,220 --> 00:01:52,020
[Episode 4]

24
00:01:57,380 --> 00:01:59,460
What a bunch of weirdos.

25
00:02:24,620 --> 00:02:27,220
[Qingsong Inn]

26
00:02:43,700 --> 00:02:44,620
You are awake.

27
00:02:45,460 --> 00:02:46,340
Come and have breakfast.

28
00:02:47,340 --> 00:02:48,380
What has happened to me?

29
00:02:49,420 --> 00:02:50,420
What has happened to you?

30
00:02:51,740 --> 00:02:53,380
A few days ago, you passed out

31
00:02:54,180 --> 00:02:55,660
and my uncle saved you.

32
00:02:57,940 --> 00:02:59,900
You are lucky

33
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:01,100
to have known me.

34
00:03:01,260 --> 00:03:02,780
My uncle doesn't always save people.

35
00:03:09,100 --> 00:03:10,700
The little thing hasn't left yet.

36
00:03:25,740 --> 00:03:27,220
Do you have a death wish?

37
00:03:30,900 --> 00:03:31,540
Cuties,

38
00:03:34,380 --> 00:03:35,460
come.

39
00:03:35,940 --> 00:03:36,980
Come over here.

40
00:03:44,500 --> 00:03:45,300
Be good.

41
00:03:45,380 --> 00:03:45,860
Uncle.

42
00:03:45,860 --> 00:03:46,140
Be good.

43
00:03:46,860 --> 00:03:48,380
This is a bit disgusting.

44
00:03:48,460 --> 00:03:50,140
These disgusting things

45
00:03:50,220 --> 00:03:51,220
saved his life.

46
00:03:52,420 --> 00:03:52,700
I...

47
00:03:59,900 --> 00:04:00,740
Thank you, sir.

48
00:04:01,860 --> 00:04:03,060
Have I recovered?

49
00:04:03,220 --> 00:04:03,700
No.

50
00:04:04,860 --> 00:04:05,380
You

51
00:04:06,140 --> 00:04:07,220
are poisoned by me.

52
00:04:09,100 --> 00:04:10,020
- What?
- What?

53
00:04:12,500 --> 00:04:13,260
The reason

54
00:04:13,700 --> 00:04:15,660
why I don't always save people

55
00:04:15,860 --> 00:04:16,980
because I use poison

56
00:04:17,140 --> 00:04:18,660
to combat the patient's poison.

57
00:04:19,220 --> 00:04:20,860
To suppress your old injuries,

58
00:04:20,940 --> 00:04:23,140
I gave you
the Guts-Shattering Five Poisons.

59
00:04:23,300 --> 00:04:24,260
But I don't have a way

60
00:04:24,580 --> 00:04:25,380
to detoxify it.

61
00:04:29,420 --> 00:04:30,020
Wait.

62
00:04:30,460 --> 00:04:31,780
What does he do now?

63
00:04:32,540 --> 00:04:33,780
He can't die just like that.

64
00:04:36,860 --> 00:04:38,140
Go to this place on the map

65
00:04:39,060 --> 00:04:40,660
and look for someone called Xin Baicao.

66
00:04:40,940 --> 00:04:42,020
I claim

67
00:04:42,140 --> 00:04:44,220
that no one can escape my poison,

68
00:04:44,380 --> 00:04:45,580
while this fellow claims

69
00:04:45,620 --> 00:04:47,580
to be able to detoxify
any poison in this world.

70
00:04:49,020 --> 00:04:50,380
Go and show him

71
00:04:50,380 --> 00:04:50,980
your poisoned body.

72
00:04:51,180 --> 00:04:52,180
Naturally, he will know

73
00:04:52,180 --> 00:04:53,500
I send you there.

74
00:04:53,580 --> 00:04:55,540
He will do his very best to cure you

75
00:04:55,580 --> 00:04:57,620
to prove he is better than me.

76
00:04:59,660 --> 00:05:00,900
Once the poison is cleared

77
00:05:01,620 --> 00:05:03,220
and your old injuries flare up,

78
00:05:03,300 --> 00:05:04,180
he might think

79
00:05:04,180 --> 00:05:05,860
it's a trick of mine

80
00:05:06,020 --> 00:05:07,380
and will save you again.

81
00:05:11,060 --> 00:05:12,060
Does

82
00:05:12,700 --> 00:05:13,980
Xin Baicao, the King of Medicine,

83
00:05:14,060 --> 00:05:14,940
really exist?

84
00:05:15,820 --> 00:05:16,460
Can he

85
00:05:17,180 --> 00:05:18,380
heal Changfeng?

86
00:05:20,740 --> 00:05:21,580
How would I know?

87
00:05:27,500 --> 00:05:28,900
[I'll poison you to death]
I do poisoning.

88
00:05:29,020 --> 00:05:29,900
I'm not a physician.

89
00:05:31,700 --> 00:05:32,500
Go now.

90
00:05:32,580 --> 00:05:33,900
You have ten more days left.

91
00:05:35,340 --> 00:05:36,300
Ten days?

92
00:05:36,980 --> 00:05:37,860
After that,

93
00:05:38,100 --> 00:05:39,140
the Guts-Breaking Five Poisons
takes effect

94
00:05:39,380 --> 00:05:40,820
and you will die
in less than four hours.

95
00:05:40,940 --> 00:05:42,420
It starts to erode your guts.

96
00:05:43,140 --> 00:05:44,220
It's very painful.

97
00:05:51,180 --> 00:05:55,380
[Chaisang City]

98
00:05:55,380 --> 00:05:56,140
Thank you, sir.

99
00:05:57,060 --> 00:05:58,060
No need to thank me.

100
00:05:58,500 --> 00:05:59,700
Your life is still at risk.

101
00:06:01,420 --> 00:06:02,260
It's better.

102
00:06:02,780 --> 00:06:03,380
I used to think

103
00:06:03,380 --> 00:06:04,500
I would die quietly

104
00:06:04,660 --> 00:06:05,380
on an unfamiliar road.

105
00:06:06,220 --> 00:06:07,300
Gladly,

106
00:06:07,420 --> 00:06:08,220
Heaven shows some mercy to me.

107
00:06:08,500 --> 00:06:09,340
I have met so many heroes

108
00:06:09,340 --> 00:06:10,780
before my life ends.

109
00:06:11,020 --> 00:06:12,300
It's worth it

110
00:06:12,780 --> 00:06:13,540
even if I die now.

111
00:06:14,180 --> 00:06:15,060
Sikong Changfeng,

112
00:06:15,420 --> 00:06:16,420
my uncle

113
00:06:16,420 --> 00:06:17,380
went to great length

114
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:18,220
to bring you

115
00:06:18,220 --> 00:06:18,900
back to life.

116
00:06:19,020 --> 00:06:20,140
Don't jinx yourself.

117
00:06:20,300 --> 00:06:21,180
Stay alive

118
00:06:21,460 --> 00:06:22,660
and wait till our next encounter

119
00:06:22,780 --> 00:06:23,700
in the martial arts world.

120
00:06:24,220 --> 00:06:25,020
You are right.

121
00:06:25,540 --> 00:06:26,620
I must stay alive.

122
00:06:27,020 --> 00:06:27,860
With a steed,

123
00:06:27,980 --> 00:06:28,740
a spear,

124
00:06:28,940 --> 00:06:29,740
and a pot of liquor,

125
00:06:29,940 --> 00:06:30,780
I will roam around

126
00:06:30,780 --> 00:06:31,620
freely.

127
00:06:31,900 --> 00:06:32,500
I wish you the same.

128
00:06:33,020 --> 00:06:34,100
Go further,

129
00:06:34,220 --> 00:06:35,180
see more of the martial arts world,

130
00:06:35,340 --> 00:06:35,940
and fulfill your promise

131
00:06:35,940 --> 00:06:37,220
of the girl you like.

132
00:06:39,500 --> 00:06:40,140
Of course.

133
00:06:47,100 --> 00:06:47,820
Take this.

134
00:06:53,740 --> 00:06:54,380
Until next time.

135
00:06:55,420 --> 00:06:56,260
Until next time.

136
00:07:21,620 --> 00:07:23,420
Stay alive, Sikong Changfeng.

137
00:07:29,300 --> 00:07:30,180
He should

138
00:07:30,380 --> 00:07:32,420
die honorably in the martial arts world.

139
00:07:33,620 --> 00:07:34,300
Uncle,

140
00:07:35,060 --> 00:07:36,620
do you think

141
00:07:36,820 --> 00:07:38,260
I should also die honorably
in the martial arts world?

142
00:07:39,700 --> 00:07:41,060
What are you talking about?
Of course not!

143
00:07:41,420 --> 00:07:42,300
Say touchwood!

144
00:07:43,060 --> 00:07:43,620
Touchwood.

145
00:07:45,060 --> 00:07:46,260
Then, how will I end up?

146
00:07:46,500 --> 00:07:47,820
You will die pathetically

147
00:07:47,820 --> 00:07:48,700
by your parents' spanking.

148
00:07:49,820 --> 00:07:50,380
Uncle,

149
00:07:50,620 --> 00:07:51,500
let's make a deal.

150
00:07:52,380 --> 00:07:52,860
No.

151
00:07:53,260 --> 00:07:53,940
I haven't said it yet.

152
00:07:53,940 --> 00:07:54,620
Let's go.

153
00:08:18,540 --> 00:08:19,340
Ye Xiaofan,

154
00:08:19,660 --> 00:08:20,740
it's time for lunch.

155
00:08:26,780 --> 00:08:28,380
So noisy.

156
00:08:31,580 --> 00:08:32,420
What do we have today?

157
00:08:32,900 --> 00:08:34,260
Don't simply touch my head.

158
00:08:34,500 --> 00:08:35,620
My sister said

159
00:08:36,020 --> 00:08:37,580
I couldn't grow tall
if you kept touching my head.

160
00:08:37,700 --> 00:08:39,140
It's not true.

161
00:08:39,460 --> 00:08:40,300
I can examine skeletons.

162
00:08:40,580 --> 00:08:41,660
I can tell

163
00:08:41,780 --> 00:08:43,020
you won't grow tall

164
00:08:43,220 --> 00:08:43,900
whether or not

165
00:08:44,020 --> 00:08:44,780
I touch you.

166
00:08:46,580 --> 00:08:47,380
If you say that again,

167
00:08:47,900 --> 00:08:49,260
your big bun

168
00:08:49,340 --> 00:08:50,500
will become mine.

169
00:08:52,220 --> 00:08:53,980
You sleep all-day

170
00:08:54,260 --> 00:08:54,900
and don't find

171
00:08:54,900 --> 00:08:56,180
a proper job.

172
00:08:56,380 --> 00:08:57,100
You won't

173
00:08:57,420 --> 00:08:58,900
get a wife in the future.

174
00:08:58,980 --> 00:08:59,660
Little brat,

175
00:08:59,660 --> 00:09:00,500
you talk

176
00:09:00,500 --> 00:09:01,660
like a mother.

177
00:09:01,900 --> 00:09:02,700
Is getting a proper job

178
00:09:02,700 --> 00:09:03,420
that important?

179
00:09:03,460 --> 00:09:04,860
Certainly.

180
00:09:07,780 --> 00:09:08,420
Well, then.

181
00:09:08,780 --> 00:09:09,500
I will do what you say.

182
00:09:12,140 --> 00:09:13,180
It seems I should

183
00:09:13,820 --> 00:09:15,460
find a proper job.

184
00:09:35,940 --> 00:09:37,260
However, I'm afraid

185
00:09:38,420 --> 00:09:40,180
I can't do that in the village.

186
00:09:41,460 --> 00:09:42,460
It's time

187
00:09:42,780 --> 00:09:44,260
to leave.

188
00:09:45,660 --> 00:09:47,820
Return to Qiandong City.

189
00:09:47,820 --> 00:09:49,260
If not, your mother will poison me.

190
00:09:49,540 --> 00:09:51,260
I doubt my mother does that better

191
00:09:51,580 --> 00:09:52,500
than you.

192
00:09:53,100 --> 00:09:55,220
I can't stand it
when she acts coquettishly.

193
00:09:56,740 --> 00:09:58,300
It's not that I'm not going back.

194
00:09:58,500 --> 00:09:59,780
I just want you to show me around
in the martial arts world

195
00:09:59,860 --> 00:10:01,140
on our way back.

196
00:10:01,300 --> 00:10:02,660
No, I don't have time.

197
00:10:02,740 --> 00:10:03,700
You are free.

198
00:10:03,940 --> 00:10:04,940
How can that be?

199
00:10:04,980 --> 00:10:05,940
I'm not free at all.

200
00:10:06,260 --> 00:10:07,860
I'm the Bodhisattva of Poison.

201
00:10:08,020 --> 00:10:09,060
I'm busy.

202
00:10:12,260 --> 00:10:13,100
Besides,

203
00:10:13,740 --> 00:10:15,860
the Swords Forest
is about to start after four years.

204
00:10:16,060 --> 00:10:17,180
I don't want to miss that.

205
00:10:17,900 --> 00:10:18,660
Swords Forest?

206
00:10:19,460 --> 00:10:20,540
What's that?

207
00:10:21,420 --> 00:10:22,580
It seems you are in such a hurry.

208
00:10:22,820 --> 00:10:23,780
Is that a great assembly?

209
00:10:25,180 --> 00:10:27,300
Swordsmen
from all over the martial arts world

210
00:10:27,420 --> 00:10:28,700
wait in the wings for four years

211
00:10:28,860 --> 00:10:30,740
for the opening of the Swords Forest.

212
00:10:30,860 --> 00:10:32,580
Does that sound grand to you?

213
00:10:35,060 --> 00:10:35,660
Uncle,

214
00:10:36,620 --> 00:10:38,060
you like me the most.

215
00:10:38,060 --> 00:10:39,060
You are the best.

216
00:10:39,420 --> 00:10:40,580
I will brew some liquor for you.

217
00:10:41,380 --> 00:10:43,060
Save it.

218
00:10:45,860 --> 00:10:46,740
Let me ask you this.

219
00:10:47,020 --> 00:10:48,100
Have your mother taught you

220
00:10:48,100 --> 00:10:48,980
any martial arts skills?

221
00:10:49,180 --> 00:10:49,860
No.

222
00:10:50,700 --> 00:10:52,140
But she got me a master

223
00:10:52,780 --> 00:10:53,780
to teach my fist techniques.

224
00:10:58,500 --> 00:10:59,540
That's enough.

225
00:10:59,820 --> 00:11:01,100
Come back.

226
00:11:01,820 --> 00:11:02,820
Who is your master?

227
00:11:03,940 --> 00:11:06,500
His name is Wangba or something.

228
00:11:07,060 --> 00:11:08,700
It's an interesting name.

229
00:11:10,140 --> 00:11:12,300
Wang Batian, the Fist Conqueror?

230
00:11:12,300 --> 00:11:13,500
Right, it's him.

231
00:11:14,060 --> 00:11:15,580
He's something to be reckoned with.

232
00:11:15,660 --> 00:11:16,380
Exactly.

233
00:11:16,620 --> 00:11:17,540
My mother also thought

234
00:11:17,620 --> 00:11:18,900
he could teach me well.

235
00:11:19,700 --> 00:11:21,380
He was working so hard,

236
00:11:21,500 --> 00:11:22,140
so

237
00:11:22,180 --> 00:11:23,460
I treated him to some liquor.

238
00:11:23,580 --> 00:11:24,580
He said he had never drunk

239
00:11:24,620 --> 00:11:26,100
such a wonderful brew in his life.

240
00:11:26,460 --> 00:11:27,860
Then, I told him

241
00:11:27,900 --> 00:11:28,740
he could drink that every day

242
00:11:28,820 --> 00:11:30,020
as long as he stopped teaching me.

243
00:11:30,180 --> 00:11:30,980
Therefore,

244
00:11:31,460 --> 00:11:32,100
my mother drove him away

245
00:11:32,380 --> 00:11:33,780
three days later.

246
00:11:35,140 --> 00:11:36,180
Do you have other masters?

247
00:11:36,460 --> 00:11:37,700
Later, she thought

248
00:11:37,900 --> 00:11:39,260
male masters were unreliable,

249
00:11:39,500 --> 00:11:40,580
so she found a female master.

250
00:11:41,060 --> 00:11:42,780
She is so beautiful.

251
00:11:42,780 --> 00:11:44,060
I still remember her name.

252
00:11:44,260 --> 00:11:45,700
Su Muqing.

253
00:11:46,020 --> 00:11:47,020
Ms. Su?

254
00:11:48,140 --> 00:11:49,060
She is indeed pretty.

255
00:11:50,020 --> 00:11:51,140
Not only that,

256
00:11:51,900 --> 00:11:53,540
she also taught me seriously

257
00:11:53,660 --> 00:11:55,260
for three days.

258
00:11:55,540 --> 00:11:56,420
Luckily,

259
00:11:56,500 --> 00:11:57,300
it was only three days.

260
00:11:57,380 --> 00:11:58,140
Why is that so?

261
00:11:58,180 --> 00:11:59,260
Since Ms. Su came,

262
00:11:59,420 --> 00:12:00,780
my father

263
00:12:00,820 --> 00:12:02,580
came to my backyard

264
00:12:02,780 --> 00:12:04,900
for three consecutive days.

265
00:12:06,660 --> 00:12:07,900
You can imagine what happened later.

266
00:12:08,660 --> 00:12:09,540
You only learned

267
00:12:09,540 --> 00:12:10,820
superficial skills.

268
00:12:11,060 --> 00:12:12,300
So, what actually

269
00:12:12,300 --> 00:12:13,420
are you good at?

270
00:12:14,060 --> 00:12:14,580
Look at me.

271
00:12:25,660 --> 00:12:26,380
What do you think?

272
00:12:29,500 --> 00:12:30,420
Even you think that's a bad one, right?

273
00:12:30,420 --> 00:12:31,060
Let's go.

274
00:12:35,060 --> 00:12:35,660
Uncle.

275
00:12:36,020 --> 00:12:36,580
Uncle.

276
00:12:37,380 --> 00:12:38,060
Uncle.

277
00:12:39,060 --> 00:12:39,700
Uncle.

278
00:12:40,020 --> 00:12:41,700
Where are you going?

279
00:12:42,420 --> 00:12:43,380
Back to Qiandong City.

280
00:12:43,540 --> 00:12:44,420
That's a shorter route.

281
00:12:44,540 --> 00:12:45,540
You can't be serious.

282
00:12:47,780 --> 00:12:49,940
Wasn't that move amazing?

283
00:12:50,260 --> 00:12:51,580
Wasn't that your father's

284
00:12:51,660 --> 00:12:52,940
qinggong technique,
Three Flying Cat Moves.

285
00:12:53,300 --> 00:12:54,540
Three Flying Cat Moves?

286
00:12:54,660 --> 00:12:55,820
It's Three Flying Swallow Moves.

287
00:12:56,060 --> 00:12:57,420
Don't underestimate this.

288
00:12:57,580 --> 00:12:59,060
It's a great fleeing skill.

289
00:13:01,380 --> 00:13:02,660
Don't go, Uncle.

290
00:13:04,300 --> 00:13:05,580
I was being mischievous before,

291
00:13:06,020 --> 00:13:07,260
but I have changed now.

292
00:13:07,540 --> 00:13:08,260
I swear,

293
00:13:08,500 --> 00:13:09,540
I'm serious this time.

294
00:13:10,940 --> 00:13:11,660
It's true

295
00:13:12,660 --> 00:13:14,300
