martial arts skills before.

296
00:13:14,580 --> 00:13:15,300
First,

297
00:13:15,660 --> 00:13:17,300
I thought fighting was boring.

298
00:13:17,900 --> 00:13:18,940
Second, as you know,

299
00:13:19,500 --> 00:13:20,900
General Ye and Yun have died.

300
00:13:21,180 --> 00:13:21,820
Grandfather didn't want me

301
00:13:21,820 --> 00:13:23,180
to suffer the Ye Family's fate.

302
00:13:23,820 --> 00:13:24,900
However, when I encountered

303
00:13:24,900 --> 00:13:26,300
the Eight Young Masters
of Beili these days

304
00:13:27,020 --> 00:13:27,540
and witnessed

305
00:13:27,540 --> 00:13:29,060
those bloodshed...

306
00:13:33,060 --> 00:13:34,300
I ask myself,

307
00:13:35,180 --> 00:13:36,020
if I could protect

308
00:13:36,020 --> 00:13:37,140
my friend

309
00:13:37,780 --> 00:13:39,020
