310
00:13:39,780 --> 00:13:41,580
Would I act like
the Eight Young Masters of Beili

311
00:13:41,780 --> 00:13:42,900
to draw my weapon

312
00:13:43,180 --> 00:13:44,700
and fight alongside him?

313
00:13:48,180 --> 00:13:48,900
Uncle.

314
00:13:50,180 --> 00:13:51,020
Who do you admire the most

315
00:13:51,420 --> 00:13:52,780
in the martial arts world?

316
00:13:53,260 --> 00:13:55,700
Needless to say, it's Mr. Li.

317
00:13:56,540 --> 00:13:57,660
Which Mr. Li are you referring to?

318
00:13:58,540 --> 00:14:00,700
Whenever the Mr. Li is mentioned,

319
00:14:01,020 --> 00:14:03,020
it must be that person.

320
00:14:03,300 --> 00:14:05,900
Mr. Li, the One-Sword Deity.

321
00:14:08,020 --> 00:14:09,420
When I was 19,

322
00:14:09,940 --> 00:14:11,300
I was fortunate to witness

323
00:14:11,540 --> 00:14:13,140
the darting sword from beyond

324
00:14:13,660 --> 00:14:16,180
with my own eyes in Tianqi City.

325
00:14:16,220 --> 00:14:18,220
Five invincible swordsmen from Nanjue

326
00:14:18,220 --> 00:14:20,300
challenged Mr. Li to a duel.

327
00:14:20,460 --> 00:14:21,780
They intended to tire him out
through attrition warfare.

328
00:14:21,860 --> 00:14:24,100
However, Mr. Li defeated them
with only a sword.

329
00:14:24,260 --> 00:14:26,260
From that day on,

330
00:14:26,460 --> 00:14:28,180
no one from Nanjue ever dares

331
00:14:28,180 --> 00:14:31,020
to challenge anyone from Beili
to sword fights.

332
00:14:33,940 --> 00:14:35,940
Naturally, Mr. Li triumphed

333
00:14:36,060 --> 00:14:37,380
