338
00:14:48,740 --> 00:14:50,060
That's cool.

339
00:14:50,700 --> 00:14:52,140
No wonder people said
Beili wields swords,

340
00:14:52,220 --> 00:14:53,220
while Nanjue holds blades.

341
00:14:53,340 --> 00:14:54,860
Turns out they have lost their guts
to practice swordsmanship skills.

342
00:14:55,260 --> 00:14:56,580
Everyone in Beili

343
00:14:56,700 --> 00:14:57,860
practices swordsmanship skills.

344
00:14:58,100 --> 00:15:00,340
