348
00:15:05,820 --> 00:15:06,420
What?

349
00:15:06,940 --> 00:15:07,540
Any problem with that?

350
00:15:07,540 --> 00:15:08,220
No.

351
00:15:11,860 --> 00:15:14,100
All right. I made up my mind.

352
00:15:14,620 --> 00:15:16,700
I want to practice swordsmanship.

353
