355
00:15:20,420 --> 00:15:21,740
It's Swords Forest we are going to.

356
00:15:22,060 --> 00:15:23,140
How can I not find one there?

357
00:15:26,340 --> 00:15:26,860
I see.

358
00:15:26,860 --> 00:15:28,540
I didn't see this coming.

359
00:15:31,220 --> 00:15:32,220
Baili.

360
00:15:34,860 --> 00:15:35,420
All right.

361
00:15:35,940 --> 00:15:36,580
