421
00:17:37,700 --> 00:17:38,740
I wonder

422
00:17:39,980 --> 00:17:41,460
if she has met someone else.

423
00:17:42,580 --> 00:17:44,220
Why don't you go and find her?

424
00:17:47,580 --> 00:17:48,220
I will.

425
00:17:50,220 --> 00:17:51,020
It will be

426
00:17:51,020 --> 00:17:52,580
after doing something I must do.

427
00:17:54,900 --> 00:17:55,580
Very soon.

428
00:17:56,980 --> 00:17:58,540
Well, stop here.

429
00:18:00,300 --> 00:18:01,140
Ye Xiaofan,

