444
00:18:26,420 --> 00:18:27,340
A faraway city

445
00:18:27,540 --> 00:18:29,140
called Tianqi.

446
00:18:29,620 --> 00:18:30,460
Tianqi?

447
00:18:30,740 --> 00:18:31,740
Isn't that the capital

448
00:18:31,740 --> 00:18:32,780
of Beili?

449
00:18:33,060 --> 00:18:34,100
