450
00:18:34,180 --> 00:18:35,820
I only read it from books.

451
00:18:35,940 --> 00:18:36,740
Ye Xiaofan,

452
00:18:37,060 --> 00:18:38,380
why are you going there?

453
00:18:38,820 --> 00:18:40,260
I'm going to Tianqi

454
00:18:40,460 --> 00:18:41,980
to achieve something big.

455
00:18:42,900 --> 00:18:43,660
Perhaps

456
00:18:43,980 --> 00:18:44,820
