00:24:54,580 --> 00:24:55,500
Not now.

583
00:24:56,340 --> 00:24:57,700
There are four levels of swords.

584
00:24:57,980 --> 00:24:59,740
First, the Mountain.

585
00:24:59,940 --> 00:25:01,340
As high as a mountain,

586
00:25:01,460 --> 00:25:03,780
unreachable by ordinary swords.

587
00:25:05,620 --> 00:25:07,420
Second, the Ocean.

588
00:25:12,580 --> 00:25:14,940
All rivers converge
into the boundless ocean.

589
00:25:15,220 --> 00:25:17,140
Merging one hundred Mountain swords

590
00:25:17,220 --> 00:25:18,740
to form the very one.

591
00:25:20,460 --> 00:25:21,500
Now, the Ocean sword.

592
00:25:21,740 --> 00:25:23,380
Everyone, please.

593
00:25:24,180 --> 00:25:26,260
Third, the Cloud Sky.

594
00:25:26,860 --> 00:25:27,900
Above the ocean,

595
00:25:28,020 --> 00:25:30,460
clouds in the ninth heaven
overlook the earth.

596
00:25:30,860 --> 00:25:33,980
There's only one in ten thousand swords.

597
00:25:35,340 --> 00:25:37,460
Fourth, the Celestial.

598
00:25:37,860 --> 00:25:41,180
Beyond the ninth heaven,
a celestial palace resides.

599
00:25:41,700 --> 00:25:45,020
It's a sword from beyond.

600
00:25:45,580 --> 00:25:47,100
Whether or not
it will emerge in the Swords Forest

601
00:25:47,620 --> 00:25:48,780
depends on your luck.

602
00:25:48,780 --> 00:25:49,740
If so...

603
00:25:50,940 --> 00:25:52,060
Given

604
00:25:52,180 --> 00:25:53,860
my swordsmanship skills,

605
00:25:54,380 --> 00:25:56,060
claiming an Ocean

606
00:25:56,220 --> 00:25:57,540
is not a problem.

607
00:25:57,740 --> 00:25:59,260
You should at least
get a Cloud Sky sword.

608
00:26:00,460 --> 00:26:02,180
In that case, I need to use poison.

609
00:26:08,540 --> 00:26:09,500
Is there any sword you like?

610
00:26:09,660 --> 00:26:10,460
I only know

611
00:26:10,460 --> 00:26:11,940
Cloud Sky lies above Ocean,

612
00:26:12,140 --> 00:26:13,500
and a Celestial one
ranks highest of all.

613
00:26:13,780 --> 00:26:14,940
Needless to say, I want the best sword.

614
00:26:15,220 --> 00:26:16,500
If not, how else can I gain fame?

615
00:26:18,100 --> 00:26:18,740
Well said.

616
00:26:21,780 --> 00:26:22,980
Who are you?

617
00:26:23,460 --> 00:26:25,380
[Wang Yixing, principal disciple]
I'm Wang Yixing from Mount Wangcheng.

618
00:26:25,380 --> 00:26:26,340
[of Lyu Suzhen from Mount Wangcheng]

619
00:26:26,940 --> 00:26:28,620
The disciple of Lyu Suzhen.

620
00:26:29,500 --> 00:26:31,420
Setting aside
whether he spoke well or not,

621
00:26:31,980 --> 00:26:33,380
his naive ambition

622
00:26:33,380 --> 00:26:35,300
to rise to fame

623
00:26:35,660 --> 00:26:37,140
is putting me on the spot.

624
00:26:38,260 --> 00:26:39,020
Mr. Wen,

625
00:26:39,940 --> 00:26:40,860
with due respect,

626
00:26:41,140 --> 00:26:41,820
he should

627
00:26:42,900 --> 00:26:44,180
claim the sword by himself.

628
00:26:44,580 --> 00:26:45,500
Mister,

629
00:26:46,180 --> 00:26:46,900
what did you say?

630
00:26:47,180 --> 00:26:48,140
Who claims the sword?

631
00:26:49,180 --> 00:26:49,940
I'm saying

632
00:26:50,060 --> 00:26:52,060
that it's better
if you claim the sword by yourself.

633
00:27:01,500 --> 00:27:02,380
Look at him.

634
00:27:03,140 --> 00:27:03,780
I'm sure

635
00:27:03,780 --> 00:27:05,340
he will get beaten up
