638
00:27:09,260 --> 00:27:10,540
Don't jump to the conclusion yet,
Mr. Wen.

639
00:27:11,060 --> 00:27:11,940
I think

640
00:27:12,500 --> 00:27:13,500
this young man

641
00:27:13,980 --> 00:27:16,500
might get a fine sword.

642
00:27:24,980 --> 00:27:26,700
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

643
00:27:32,180 --> 00:27:33,940
You can't be drunk, can you?

644
00:27:36,900 --> 00:27:37,660
The Mountain sword

645
00:27:38,060 --> 00:27:38,940
and the Ocean sword

646
00:27:39,260 --> 00:27:40,460
have each found their owners.

647
00:27:41,100 --> 00:27:42,220
The next sword

648
00:27:43,100 --> 00:27:44,820
is of Cloud Sky level.

649
00:27:45,740 --> 00:27:47,940
I named it Fire Divine.

650
00:28:15,140 --> 00:28:16,500
It's a shard of the ablaze sword,
Grand Sun,

651
00:28:16,660 --> 00:28:18,780
use by the Kunlun Sword Deity
