652
00:28:19,740 --> 00:28:20,820
To be more precise,

653
00:28:20,940 --> 00:28:22,620
it's born out of the Grand Sun.

654
00:28:22,620 --> 00:28:23,980
It belongs to the Celestial Palace,

655
00:28:24,260 --> 00:28:25,540
but alas, falls from the ninth heaven.

656
00:28:25,780 --> 00:28:26,460
