657
00:28:27,060 --> 00:28:27,740
I'm down.

658
00:28:27,860 --> 00:28:28,420
Me too.

659
00:28:28,540 --> 00:28:29,220
I'm coming.

660
00:28:36,780 --> 00:28:37,700
