among all current disciples.

674
00:29:24,460 --> 00:29:25,700
You are drunk.

675
00:29:25,940 --> 00:29:26,700
This is Sword Liquor.

676
00:29:26,700 --> 00:29:28,260
It's different from ordinary liquor.

677
00:29:30,940 --> 00:29:32,260
Wang Yixing, the principal disciple

678
00:29:32,420 --> 00:29:34,620
