688
00:29:49,540 --> 00:29:50,540
for my junior brother.

689
00:29:50,900 --> 00:29:51,460
Everyone,

690
00:29:51,900 --> 00:29:52,620
thank you.

691
00:29:54,300 --> 00:29:55,300
He mentioned

692
00:29:55,380 --> 00:29:56,460
"swords of a higher level".

693
00:29:56,460 --> 00:29:57,100
Exactly.

694
00:29:57,180 --> 00:29:58,300
Wushuang City hasn't started yet.

695
00:29:58,340 --> 00:29:59,300
Is there really a fourth-level sword?

696
00:30:03,180 --> 00:30:04,020
The fourth level,

697
00:30:04,500 --> 00:30:05,780
Celestial Level Sword.

698
00:30:07,380 --> 00:30:08,780
Please grant me

699
00:30:09,580 --> 00:30:12,020
this sword from beyond.

