709
00:31:07,900 --> 00:31:08,860
and let it triumph

710
00:31:09,660 --> 00:31:11,060
the Record of Famous Swords.

711
00:31:16,020 --> 00:31:17,060
This is a great sword.

712
00:31:17,740 --> 00:31:19,300
I want it.

713
00:31:25,980 --> 00:31:27,020
You fool.

714
00:31:27,220 --> 00:31:28,060
Do you want your uncle,

715
00:31:28,060 --> 00:31:28,660
