717
00:31:36,260 --> 00:31:38,500
I, Song Yanhui of Wushuang City,
wish to claim this sword.

718
00:31:40,180 --> 00:31:41,300
Who will be my rival?

719
00:31:41,460 --> 00:31:43,460
I doubt someone will compete
