734
00:32:33,220 --> 00:32:34,340
Such agility.

735
00:32:53,420 --> 00:32:54,740
An innate swordsman.

736
00:32:55,100 --> 00:32:56,060
You are indeed strong.

737
00:32:56,940 --> 00:32:57,700
But I am

738
00:32:59,020 --> 00:32:59,780
stronger.

739
00:33:00,180 --> 00:33:00,780
Uncle,

740
00:33:01,300 --> 00:33:02,060
