743
00:33:05,940 --> 00:33:06,820
However, the difference

744
00:33:06,940 --> 00:33:08,220
is that the guy from Wushuang City

745
00:33:08,300 --> 00:33:09,860
is already out of his depth,

746
00:33:10,700 --> 00:33:11,900
while Ye Dingzhi

747
00:33:12,420 --> 00:33:13,900
hasn't fully exerted his strength.

748
00:33:13,980 --> 00:33:16,540
He possesses such strength
at this young age.

749
00:33:16,540 --> 00:33:17,860
That's not easy.

750
00:33:21,620 --> 00:33:22,860
Wushuang City actually loses.

751
00:33:22,980 --> 00:33:23,420
This is unbelievable.

752
00:33:23,980 --> 00:33:24,860
How did this happen?

753
00:33:29,620 --> 00:33:30,820
I concede defeat.

754
00:33:31,500 --> 00:33:32,380
Thank you.

755
00:33:40,500 --> 00:33:41,500
Hold on.

756
00:33:43,300 --> 00:33:44,260
Baili!

757
00:33:59,820 --> 00:34:00,460
I

758
00:34:01,740 --> 00:34:03,060
want that sword too.

759
00:34:11,020 --> 00:34:12,460
