763
00:34:34,140 --> 00:34:34,780
No.

764
00:34:36,580 --> 00:34:37,340
No, we don't.

765
00:34:39,780 --> 00:34:40,940
Then why did you...

766
00:34:41,180 --> 00:34:42,180
You want to claim the sword,

767
00:34:43,580 --> 00:34:44,540
but where is yours?

768
00:34:45,100 --> 00:34:45,980
My...

