773
00:35:01,260 --> 00:35:02,420
What a disgrace.

774
00:35:06,300 --> 00:35:07,900
I have one now.

775
00:35:11,540 --> 00:35:13,780
He's just as silly as he was.

776
00:35:17,420 --> 00:35:19,140
Hold on. I remember it now.

777
00:35:19,660 --> 00:35:21,260
Why do I think

778
00:35:21,380 --> 00:35:23,740
you look familiar?

779
00:35:25,060 --> 00:35:26,100
Baili Dongjun,

780
00:35:26,700 --> 00:35:27,660
are you trying

781
00:35:27,660 --> 00:35:28,740
