782
00:35:31,860 --> 00:35:32,900
You came to the wrong place.

783
00:36:07,900 --> 00:36:08,900
He is great.

784
00:36:22,580 --> 00:36:23,580
Are you not drawing your sword?

785
00:36:24,300 --> 00:36:26,620
I don't know any sword techniques.

786
00:36:49,140 --> 00:36:50,780
Young man, come down. Just surrender.

787
00:36:50,980 --> 00:36:52,500
- Exactly.
- Exactly.

788
00:36:52,540 --> 00:36:54,460
Just quit and come down.

789
00:36:54,860 --> 00:36:56,780
Don't get hurt. Stop fighting.

790
00:37:00,980 --> 00:37:02,780
It seems that you are no match for me.

791
00:37:04,300 --> 00:37:05,500
This idiot

792
00:37:05,940 --> 00:37:07,140
must be slacking off during practice

793
00:37:07,460 --> 00:37:08,780
like he did back then.

794
00:37:14,860 --> 00:37:15,660
Sword?

795
00:37:17,380 --> 00:37:19,580
Can I wield a sword?

796
00:37:42,580 --> 00:37:43,780
Master,

797
00:37:44,220 --> 00:37:46,580
