803
00:38:04,780 --> 00:38:06,100
On this earth,

804
00:38:06,420 --> 00:38:07,860
from past to future,

805
00:38:08,540 --> 00:38:10,020
no one with this technique

806
00:38:10,140 --> 00:38:12,460
will ever emerge again.

807
00:38:16,100 --> 00:38:17,500
If someone

808
00:38:17,780 --> 00:38:19,020
does,

809
00:38:19,420 --> 00:38:20,860
it will only be from the Baili Family.

810
00:38:35,300 --> 00:38:36,460
I have recalled it.

811
00:38:43,700 --> 00:38:45,020
I know swordsmanship.

812
00:39:08,860 --> 00:39:09,540
That's...

