00:39:17,020 --> 00:39:19,380
♪Overcoming the boundary of confusion♪

814
00:39:19,740 --> 00:39:22,100
♪Holding onto my life
in the face of death threats♪

815
00:39:22,420 --> 00:39:25,540
♪I look into this dark night♪

816
00:39:27,700 --> 00:39:30,060
♪Never once has my soul extinguished♪

817
00:39:30,420 --> 00:39:32,780
♪Wielding this passion♪

818
00:39:33,100 --> 00:39:36,740
♪My spirit is growing
to reach full swing♪

819
00:39:37,940 --> 00:39:40,860
♪Slashing the mountain
and the ocean apart♪

820
00:39:41,100 --> 00:39:43,260
♪Answering the true call on a sword♪

821
00:39:43,620 --> 00:39:44,980
♪I'm the chosen one
