829
00:39:59,900 --> 00:40:00,940
It was exactly the same

830
00:40:00,940 --> 00:40:02,700
as Mr. Baili's.

831
00:40:03,420 --> 00:40:08,180
♪Soaring towards the sky,
the sword reigns all♪

832
00:40:08,180 --> 00:40:08,860
But his moves

833
