843
00:40:42,780 --> 00:40:44,300
Heaven's Path.

844
00:40:45,220 --> 00:40:48,980
Back then, Gu Chen,
the Scholar Deity of Western Chu sings

845
00:40:49,100 --> 00:40:51,140
