00:41:06,780 --> 00:41:08,580
became a lost art.

855
00:41:16,620 --> 00:41:17,300
That's my nephew.

856
00:41:19,780 --> 00:41:20,580
My nephew.

857
00:41:21,300 --> 00:41:22,580
I didn't expect

858
00:41:23,860 --> 00:41:26,140
that the Marquis of Zhenxi's Mansion

859
00:41:26,540 --> 00:41:28,980
would be more bolder than I imagined.

860
00:41:30,100 --> 00:41:31,260
I thought

861
00:41:31,780 --> 00:41:33,380
